                            A Site-19 Christmas Carol
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<div style="text-align: center;">
<blockquote>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> The following script, all seventy-two pages of it, was found discarded in a Site-19 cafeteria trash can.</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>Additional Note:</strong> Please remember that Site-19 printer ink is designated for Foundation work <em><strong>ONLY</strong></em>.</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
