<p><strong>Narrator 2:</strong> As quickly as they did rise into the night sky, so did they descend before a long, dirt road surrounded by trees. The darkness of Bright's home had vanished, and was replaced with the light of a cold, clear winter day, with fresh snow upon the ground.</p>
<p><strong>Bright:</strong> I&#8230; wait! I know where this is! This is the road through the country to Site-17! This is where my first assignment was, where&#8212; how long ago was it? I would've just been a kid.</p>
